OL,3,CTower block 'structural issues' were
OL,4,Cflagged to council year before
OL,5,Cevacuation
OL,7,FStructural issues at the Barton House
OL,8,Ftower block in Bristol were flagged to
OL,9,Fthe city council in August 2022, more
OL,10,Fthan a year before the building was
OL,11,Feventually evacuated.
OL,13,FCouncil staff decided the risks
OL,14,Fdetailed in a report "could be
OL,15,Fmitigated", but then in November 2023
OL,16,Fengineers reviewed the report and
OL,17,Fsounded the alarm.
