OL,3,CTower block 'structural issues' were
OL,4,Cflagged to council year before
OL,5,Cevacuation
OL,7,FMore than 400 people - including
OL,8,Faround 100 children - their homes in
OL,9,Fthe tower block on the evening of
OL,10,FTuesday 14 November.
OL,12,FCouncil bosses were told a fire in a
OL,13,Fsingle flat could lead to the building
OL,14,Fcollapsing.
OL,16,FNow it has been revealed that the
OL,17,Fgovernment wrote a letter to councils
OL,18,Fin 2017 urging them to check their
OL,19,Flarge-panel system buildings after
OL,20,Flarge cracks appeared on tower blocks
OL,21,Fin London built in the same way.
