OL,4,Cflagged to council year before
OL,5,Cevacuation
OL,7,FThe council commissioned a report into
OL,8,FBarton House and other LPS buildings.
OL,10,FHowever, it didn't receive this report
OL,11,Funtil August 2022, when staff decided
OL,12,Fthat the risks at Barton House could
OL,13,Fbe managed.
OL,15,FArup, an engineering consultancy, then
OL,16,Fconducted a peer review of the survey
OL,17,Fin November 2023 and came to a very
OL,18,Fdifferent conclusion.
