OL,7,FGreen Party co-leader and Councillor
OL,8,FCarla Denyer believes the severe
OL,9,Fimpact of the evacuation on residents
OL,10,Fcould have been avoided.
OL,12,FMs Denyer said: "It seems like the
OL,13,Fsudden upheaval of residents leaving
OL,14,FBarton absolutely could have been
OL,15,Favoided.
