OL,7,F"The impact has been severe on their
OL,8,Fmental health. I was visiting the
OL,9,Fhotel where many of them were staying
OL,10,Fat the weekend. I spoke to the mum of
OL,11,Fthe teenage girl who was self harming
OL,12,Fand speak to another mum whose pre-
OL,13,Fteen boy was not eating properly and
OL,14,Fcannot go to school.
OL,16,F"I'm not a mental health expert but it
OL,17,Fseems like those young people are
OL,18,Fsuffering from the trauma as a result
OL,19,Fof the experience."
