OL,7,FA written response to a public
OL,8,Fquestion at a full council meeting on
OL,9,F9 January revealed new information
OL,10,Fshowing that the council knew about
OL,11,Fstructural issues at Barton House, but
OL,12,Fchose not to evacuate the tower block
OL,13,Funtil well over a year later.
OL,15,FThe response said: "We remain in
OL,16,Fconversation with the government about
OL,17,Ftheir 2017 letter and the actions
OL,18,Ftaken since.
