OL,7,F"Different kinds of surveys have been
OL,8,Fundertaken at Barton House and other
OL,9,Fhigh-rise blocks since that time, with
OL,10,Fthe information on each acted on to
OL,11,Fdeliver improvements where necessary.
OL,13,F"The council commissioned a structural
OL,14,Fsurvey of Barton House and other LPS,
OL,15,For LPS-similar constructed buildings,
OL,16,Ffollowing receipt of the 2017 letter
OL,17,Ffrom the government on the safety of
OL,18,Flarge panel system buildings.
