OL,7,F"This report was received in August
OL,8,F2022. This report flagged structural
OL,9,Fissues at Barton House.
OL,11,F"On receipt of the report, Bristol
OL,12,Fofficers determined that the risks
OL,13,Fpresented could be mitigated.
