OL,7,F"Indeed, at the time there were
OL,8,Falready mitigations in place,
OL,9,Fincluding no piped gas supply to flats
OL,10,Fand a waking watch in place. In
OL,11,FNovember 2023, this report was peer-
OL,12,Freviewed by Arup which significantly
OL,13,Fescalated the structural risks at
OL,14,FBarton House."
OL,16,FA freedom of information request for
OL,17,Fthe report has been refused. The
OL,18,Fcouncil said it will be published
OL,19,Fonline once the final report from the
OL,20,Flatest building survey has been
OL,21,Fcompleted.
