OL,7,FMore detailed surveys have since
OL,8,Frevealed the problems were not as
OL,9,Fsevere as thought, and safety work,
OL,10,Fincluding the installation of a
OL,11,Fcentral fire alarm system, additional
OL,12,Ffireproofing in 42 flats, and testing
OL,13,Ffor Legionella bacteria is now
OL,14,Funderway to make the building safe for
OL,15,Fresidents to return
OL,17,FDespite this, nearly half of the
OL,18,Fhouseholds at the protest on Friday 26
OL,19,FJanuary said they do not want to
OL,20,Freturn.
